hasMenuItem.name: Crispy Hot Chick'UN Burger
hasMenuItem.description:
Our plant-based chick'UN patty in our vegan bun, with fresh lettuce, flaming sauce and vegan cheese.
The meat portion includes water, soy protein (soy lecithin), coconut oil, cellulose, methylcellulose, yeast extracts, dehydrated vegetables, sugar, maltodextrin, spices, salt and natural flavours. The Chick'UN coating contains water, wheat flour, salt, sugar, yeast, vegetable oils (canola, olive), wheat gluten, natural colours (sunset yellow FCF, tartrazine), modified corn starch, spices (paprika, celery, pepper, turmeric), guar gum, yeast extract and canola oil.
Allergens: Contains cereals containing gluten (wheat) and soy.

hasMenuItem.name: Papdi Chaat
hasMenuItem.description: Chaat Papdi is a popular and flavorful Indian street food that tantalizes the taste buds with its unique combination of textures and tastes. This savory and tangy dish is a delightful melange of crispy fried dough wafers (papdi), boiled potatoes, chickpeas, yogurt, and an assortment of spices and chutneys.

hasMenuItem.name: Chole Kulche (Delhi Style)
hasMenuItem.description: Chole kulche is a popular North Indian street food dish that combines spiced chickpeas (chole) with soft, fluffy bread called kulche. The chickpeas are cooked in a tangy, flavorful gravy made with tomatoes, onions, and a blend of spices. The kulche, usually made from refined flour, is baked or cooked on a tawa until golden and crisp.

review.reviewBody: Always delicious!! i love everything i've tried here. my fav is the Maple Butter Crepe (V) and Classic Crispy Chick'UN Burger, those are my go-to!

Mighty Crispy Chickun Burger - Spicy  it was soggy when it came but the flavors were okay.

NEW!! Vegan Butter Chickun Poutine - the taste was not good. it hardly felt like butter chicken. the fries were cold and soy pieces wasn't  flavorful at all
Delicious, good value. The Green smoothie was an especially nice surprise, super refreshing and delicious
Sweet Chilli Crispy ChickUN Burger & Masala Fries are awesome
Wow, amazing food! Incredible butter chicken sauce and desserts! I can't have dairy because it makes me really sick so this place is awesome for me! 10/10 will order again!
